### API Endpoint Test Suite
### GET /api/tasting-notes/:id

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/tasting-notes

### AUTHENTICATION: 
### 1. Run the login request in auth.http to get an access token
### 2. Update the accessToken.


### Test 1: Get existing tasting note
### Expected: 200 OK with tasting note data
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{testNoteId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Test 2: Get second existing tasting note
### Expected: 200 OK with different tasting note data
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{testNoteId2}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Test 3: Get non-existent tasting note (valid UUID)
### Expected: 404 Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{nonExistentNoteId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Test 4: Invalid UUID format - not a UUID
### Expected: 400 Bad Request
GET {{baseUrl}}/not-a-uuid
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Test 5: Invalid UUID format - malformed UUID
### Expected: 400 Bad Request
GET {{baseUrl}}/123-456-789
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Test 6: Invalid UUID format - partial UUID
### Expected: 400 Bad Request
GET {{baseUrl}}/123e4567-e89b-12d3
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Test 7: Valid UUID with different format (uppercase)
### Expected: 404 Not Found (UUID valid but doesn't exist)
GET {{baseUrl}}/123E4567-E89B-12D3-A456-426614174000
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
